Definition: the means whereby some act is accomplished
Example: my greed was the instrument of my destruction; science has given us new tools to fight disease
Synonyms: adj, all, helpful, instrumental, verb, possession, tool, means, the, whereby, some, act, is, accomplished, my, greed, was, of, destruction, science, has, given, us, new, tools, to, fight, disease
Category: noun.act
